description:
Two animations. I messed up on the first. I thought I set it for 60 minutes but only set it to capture 10 minutes.

Processed in IMPPG (sharpen, tone curves)
Photoshop (batched processed: Rotate, high pass, crop, denoise, block the disk)
Frame rate 15 FPS

Version A 10 minutes (still nice activity(
Version B 60 minutes

The second animation is 60 minutes duration
500 frames (40FPS), captured every 40 seconds for 1 hour
Stacked 50 frames

This was my first animation with the used/new to me ZWO 1600. I am NOT use to these Newtonian rings. I used my tilt adapter and guess I need to work on it further.  Overall I am pretty happy with the results.
title: Nice prom animation
